content:
Why has the behavior of my VS Code changed so that when I start debugging a program it begins debugging and shows output in the "Integrated Terminal" instead of the "Debug Console", which was the previous default behavior? Here is my `launch.json` configuration:

```json
{
    "version": "0.2.0",
    "configurations": [{
            "name": "Python: Current File",
            "type": "python",
            "request": "launch",
            "program": "${file}"
        }
    ]
}
```

I would like to return to the previous setting where the output was displayed only in the "Debug Console". Can anyone help me with this?
